description: Qliro AB operates as a financial technology company that engages in the development of payment solution platform. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 208 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-10-02. This financial technology organization offers online payment solutions, including a complete checkout solution, to e-retailers and their customers in the Nordic region, as well as digital financial services to consumers in Sweden.
name: Qliro AB
